OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FReuse shop opens third     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbranch in Bristol for      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Funwanted Christmas gifts   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A waste company is planning to open its
OL,6, third reuse shop to help reduce the    
OL,7, amount of waste created during and     
OL,8, after the Christmas period.            
OL,10,FBristol Waste has opened two shops in  
OL,11,FAvonmouth and St Phillips and is set to
OL,12,Fopen a third in Hartcliffe in spring.  
OL,14,FAccording to the group, waste increases
OL,15,Fby 20 percent over Christmas and has   
OL,16,Frisen in general during the pandemic.  
OL,18,FA Bristol Waste volunteer said people  
OL,19,Fcould try changing their "Christmas    
OL,20,Frituals" to support the reuse economy. 
